                <div class="text">
                    <p>bPanel is built with extensibility in mind. If you've got a blockchain app you've always wanted, bPanel is your shortcut to delivery.</p>
                    <p>Every part of bPanel is customizable. Want your own plugin? The bPanel CLI tool will help spec 
                    out the initial skeleton with <strong>bpanel-cli create</strong></p>
                    <a class="section-link" href="/docs/intro_plugin.html">Plugin Docs</a>
                </div>
            </div>
